OL,5, The US justice department has moved to 
OL,6, end the sentencing disparity between   
OL,7, crack and powder cocaine offences,     
OL,8, ending a policy widely seen as racist. 
OL,10,FAttorney General Merrick Garland said  
OL,11,Fin a memo that the policy "drives      
OL,12,Funwarranted racial disparities in our  
OL,13,Fcriminal justice system".              
OL,15,FPresident Joe Biden had backed ditching
OL,16,Fthe sentencing guidelines he himself   
OL,17,Fcrafted as a senator decades ago.      
OL,19,FThe new rule will take effect within 30
OL,20,Fdays. It does not apply retroactively. 
